title: 047 - Tony Digs Loves Skim Milk
description: On today's show, the guys read through some more #PodFacts, what sandwich you would pick if you could only choose one for the rest of your life, who would last longest if they were to be dropped in a remote area, similar to the Netflix show "Alone." The boys also debut The Boobz Brothers new theme song, give Coach Digs a call to check-in, and talk about some of the things they got in trouble for in grade school. Send in your questions to @ThePodPMI on Instagram and Twitter. Have good one, enjoy.
